<div class="note-source" id="TSJN-01-01-0231-sn">
<p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ note, notes (memoranda, fragments, &amp;c.) ]">N</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Library of Congress ]">DLC</span>). Written on several sheets and fragments of paper.</p>
<p>These notes were compiled for TJs revision of the Report on the Value of Gold and Silver Coins (the following document), q.v. Some portions of the original notes have not been printed here because either illegible or repeated in the Report itself.</p></div>
